			<h2>Pricing Information</h2>
			<img src="images/dogandcat.jpg" alt="dog and cat grooming" class="center">
			<p>We have a variety of services offered here at <a href="index.html">Puppy Cuts</a>.  Our package services always include a bath, nail trimming, ear cleaning, pad shaving and anal gland cleaning.  Beyond that we have options for either a brushing or a haircut.  We provide the bath and brush package to both dogs and cats.</p>
			
			<p>We have additional services that can be provided at an extra fee.  Additional services include: nail trimming, teeth cleaning and flea treatment.  Below are a list of prices for our packages and individual services.  Note that the ranges in price depend on size of dog.
			
